WEBVTT

00:00:08.940 --> 00:00:09.940
Fuu?

00:00:13.540 --> 00:00:14.930
We need to go shopping.

00:00:16.340 --> 00:00:17.340
I know.

00:00:17.570 --> 00:00:19.490
It's the anniversary of
your dad's death, right?

00:00:27.620 --> 00:00:28.620
Go get ready.

00:00:36.530 --> 00:00:37.650
I can go by myself.

00:00:37.880 --> 00:00:39.000
That's how it is every year.

00:00:41.930 --> 00:00:43.030
Let me come with you.

00:01:03.500 --> 00:01:06.700
"The Boy Next World My Destiny"
(Episode 7)

00:01:47.500 --> 00:01:49.099
(Yutori: Fuu, are you okay?)

00:01:49.100 --> 00:01:51.799
(Naruka: We're all here for you.)

00:01:51.800 --> 00:01:53.800
(Adachi: Hey, say
something! Are you alright?)

00:01:54.200 --> 00:01:57.900
(Fuu: I'm fine.)

00:02:04.850 --> 00:02:05.850
Sara-senpai?

00:02:13.700 --> 00:02:20.000
(Fuu: I'm with my boyfriend right now.)

00:02:20.090 --> 00:02:21.090
That should do it.

00:02:22.610 --> 00:02:23.610
Wow.

00:02:24.230 --> 00:02:25.430
They all got quiet right away.

00:02:36.790 --> 00:02:38.910
- Thank you for your business.
- Thanks.

00:02:39.170 --> 00:02:40.170
It's okay.

00:02:46.120 --> 00:02:47.120
I'll pay.

00:02:47.860 --> 00:02:48.860
Alright.

00:02:48.870 --> 00:02:49.690
Thank you. Come again.

00:02:49.690 --> 00:02:50.690
Let's go.

00:02:51.400 --> 00:02:52.400
Thanks.

00:02:52.890 --> 00:02:53.940
Hot, hot, hot!

00:02:55.180 --> 00:02:56.180
Give it to me.

00:03:07.200 --> 00:03:08.200
Ah.

00:03:08.950 --> 00:03:10.410
- Is it good?
- Yeah.

00:03:19.830 --> 00:03:20.830
What's next...?

00:03:23.510 --> 00:03:25.190
It's about time for a meal.

00:03:26.070 --> 00:03:27.070
Yeah.

00:03:37.620 --> 00:03:42.170
Slumming it with the poors is contagious.

00:03:46.280 --> 00:03:48.250
I'll arrange it as soon as possible.

00:03:57.910 --> 00:03:59.280
It's been a while.

00:04:00.080 --> 00:04:01.180
Auntie.

00:04:08.700 --> 00:04:11.000
(Sengokuen Chinese Pub)

00:04:20.410 --> 00:04:23.020
You must be tired from running around.

00:04:25.650 --> 00:04:27.330
I wanted to come along.

00:04:30.640 --> 00:04:33.820
I really respected your father.

00:04:36.990 --> 00:04:38.470
Even though I never met him.

00:04:48.140 --> 00:04:49.870
The Gomoku Yakisoba here...

00:04:51.600 --> 00:04:53.240
was my dad's favorite.

00:04:57.330 --> 00:04:58.630
All of this was, too.

00:04:59.950 --> 00:05:01.590
I buy all of this every year.

00:05:05.930 --> 00:05:07.030
Always by yourself?

00:05:09.420 --> 00:05:11.520
I just prefer to be alone on this day.

00:05:14.590 --> 00:05:15.630
It's always been that way.

00:05:48.620 --> 00:05:49.860
They don't have it here either.

00:05:54.150 --> 00:05:55.250
Is this right?

00:06:02.530 --> 00:06:03.730
Not these flowers?

00:06:05.950 --> 00:06:07.350
They were my dad's favorite.

00:06:09.350 --> 00:06:11.270
In your world, did you
buy these every year too?

00:06:16.240 --> 00:06:17.240
So that means...

00:06:17.440 --> 00:06:20.480
even in the other world, my dad is gone.

00:06:25.030 --> 00:06:27.090
But the Fuu over there is lucky.

00:06:28.020 --> 00:06:29.590
He has you by his side, Sara-senpai.

00:06:31.970 --> 00:06:33.110
Oh, sorry.

00:06:34.280 --> 00:06:36.260
I was just kidding. Just thinking out loud.

00:06:44.640 --> 00:06:46.280
The past can't be changed,

00:06:48.400 --> 00:06:50.300
but I'll always be here for you.

00:06:51.600 --> 00:06:52.600
I promise.

00:07:00.960 --> 00:07:03.490
What the hell? You said
it was an emergency...

00:07:08.750 --> 00:07:09.850
You little brat.

00:07:11.040 --> 00:07:12.140
What are you doing here?

00:07:13.970 --> 00:07:15.640
Have you seen Sara?

00:07:16.140 --> 00:07:17.850
Sara-senpai isn't coming.

00:07:19.180 --> 00:07:20.180
Huh?

00:07:20.320 --> 00:07:21.419
I asked him

00:07:21.420 --> 00:07:23.440
to get you to come here, Taiga-senpai.

00:07:25.540 --> 00:07:27.150
Come on, let's go. It's urgent.

00:07:27.390 --> 00:07:28.090
What for?

00:07:28.091 --> 00:07:31.920
The last screening of a movie I've been
wanting to see starts in 15 minutes.

00:07:32.030 --> 00:07:33.990
- No way. I never said I'd go.
- Stop complaining.

00:07:34.120 --> 00:07:35.120
This way.

00:07:41.500 --> 00:07:45.640
Why does Sara even listen to this kid?

00:07:47.010 --> 00:07:49.950
He doesn't listen to a word I say.

00:08:05.230 --> 00:08:06.290
What are you laughing at?

00:08:13.650 --> 00:08:14.650
Just pay attention.

00:08:15.640 --> 00:08:17.730
Don't blame me if you
can't follow the plot.

00:08:49.840 --> 00:08:51.080
Is this where you used to live?

00:08:51.700 --> 00:08:52.700
Yeah.

00:08:53.050 --> 00:08:54.530
I lived here until high school.

00:08:55.210 --> 00:08:56.669
I have someone look after it,

00:08:56.670 --> 00:08:58.030
so it's still pretty clean inside.

00:08:59.800 --> 00:09:00.800
Let's go in.

00:09:02.640 --> 00:09:04.620
You don't have to force a smile.

00:09:09.570 --> 00:09:11.700
You don't have to act tough around me.

00:09:14.410 --> 00:09:16.120
But I don't want anyone to know

00:09:16.870 --> 00:09:18.600
that I'm actually still hurting.

00:09:30.470 --> 00:09:31.770
I already know.

00:09:44.960 --> 00:09:45.960
Fuu?

00:09:46.760 --> 00:09:47.760
Hayato.

00:09:49.800 --> 00:09:51.350
Muscat grapes,

00:09:53.850 --> 00:09:54.850
rice crackers,

00:09:56.970 --> 00:09:58.170
fried chicken,

00:10:00.980 --> 00:10:02.180
and Gomoku Yakisoba.

00:10:03.980 --> 00:10:05.350
I brought them all today.

00:10:11.100 --> 00:10:12.100
Is this okay?

00:10:13.730 --> 00:10:14.730
Thank you.

00:10:20.950 --> 00:10:23.080
But what brings you here today?

00:10:23.330 --> 00:10:24.330
Oh.

00:10:24.630 --> 00:10:26.510
My mom told me to come check on you.

00:10:27.470 --> 00:10:29.320
Everyone misses you.

00:10:30.110 --> 00:10:32.620
Sorry, I haven't been in touch lately.

00:10:35.120 --> 00:10:37.750
I thought you'd be here
alone again this year.

00:10:38.820 --> 00:10:39.820
You surprised me.

00:10:45.370 --> 00:10:46.370
Oh.

00:10:47.040 --> 00:10:48.180
This is Hayato,

00:10:48.660 --> 00:10:49.660
my cousin.

00:10:52.520 --> 00:10:53.930
And this is Sara-senpai,

00:10:54.320 --> 00:10:55.790
my senior from university.

00:10:56.830 --> 00:10:57.830
Actually...

00:11:01.410 --> 00:11:02.640
I'm Fuu's boyfriend.

00:11:06.710 --> 00:11:08.010
Well...

00:11:10.750 --> 00:11:12.590
It seems that's not quite the case.

00:11:14.270 --> 00:11:15.790
I will be one day.

00:11:18.810 --> 00:11:19.810
I'm sure of it.

00:11:30.040 --> 00:11:31.760
I'll wait for you guys outside.

00:11:32.940 --> 00:11:33.940
Thanks.

00:12:06.200 --> 00:12:07.200
Dad,

00:12:07.530 --> 00:12:08.730
did you see that?

00:12:11.490 --> 00:12:13.610
It looks like your son has
finally fallen for someone.

00:12:19.570 --> 00:12:20.570
That was so awkward.

00:12:22.310 --> 00:12:23.510
Where are we going next?

00:12:24.490 --> 00:12:25.749
There's a restaurant nearby.

00:12:25.750 --> 00:12:27.950
How did you get Sara to listen to you?

00:12:31.440 --> 00:12:32.440
If I tell you,

00:12:32.720 --> 00:12:34.320
will you go to the movies with me again?

00:12:37.130 --> 00:12:38.130
I made a deal with him.

00:12:38.850 --> 00:12:40.799
If I got you out of the house,

00:12:40.800 --> 00:12:42.310
he'd get some alone time with Fuu.

00:12:44.360 --> 00:12:45.750
Let's go see a movie.

00:12:46.830 --> 00:12:47.830
Come on.

00:12:48.800 --> 00:12:49.800
No.

00:12:49.950 --> 00:12:50.950
You're so annoying.

00:12:51.220 --> 00:12:52.510
Stop asking me.

00:12:53.100 --> 00:12:54.100
Let's go.

00:12:54.120 --> 00:12:55.739
- No.
- Please?

00:12:55.740 --> 00:12:57.090
I said no.

00:13:00.790 --> 00:13:02.410
But you really want to see that movie.

00:13:03.310 --> 00:13:05.010
Stop reading my mind.

00:13:05.810 --> 00:13:07.010
I'm not reading it.

00:13:07.020 --> 00:13:08.780
I just hear it automatically
when I'm close.

00:13:09.670 --> 00:13:10.840
Shut up.

00:13:11.190 --> 00:13:12.820
Taiga-senpai's inner world...

00:13:15.430 --> 00:13:16.430
I figured as much.

00:13:16.930 --> 00:13:18.560
Sara-senpai is so quiet, though.

00:13:18.770 --> 00:13:20.490
You're friends, but you're total opposites.

00:13:23.420 --> 00:13:24.740
Why don't we help each other out?

00:13:27.290 --> 00:13:30.690
Get Taiga-senpai to
meet you at the theater.

00:13:31.810 --> 00:13:33.570
If you ask, he'll
definitely show up, right?

00:13:34.930 --> 00:13:35.930
Why would I do that?

00:13:37.400 --> 00:13:39.480
The day after tomorrow is the anniversary.

00:13:40.230 --> 00:13:42.200
We usually all get together that night.

00:13:42.890 --> 00:13:45.030
You don't want to be interrupted, do you?

00:13:55.670 --> 00:13:56.670
Sara.

00:13:57.420 --> 00:13:58.950
You sold me out?

00:13:59.390 --> 00:14:00.989
Yeah, I did.

00:14:00.990 --> 00:14:02.530
Aren't we childhood friends?

00:14:08.310 --> 00:14:09.790
What should we see for our next date?

00:14:27.330 --> 00:14:30.910
Let's give Fuu and uncle some space.

00:14:50.200 --> 00:14:51.200
So?

00:14:52.270 --> 00:14:53.490
Who exactly are you to Fuu?

00:14:54.850 --> 00:14:56.690
Besides that "future lover" line.

00:15:00.200 --> 00:15:04.450
I'm just...

00:15:07.480 --> 00:15:09.400
a man who wants to take care of him.

00:15:11.560 --> 00:15:12.560
What does that mean?

00:15:18.180 --> 00:15:19.440
Let me ask you this.

00:15:22.360 --> 00:15:27.380
Can you promise never to make him sad?

00:15:30.320 --> 00:15:31.320
That's...

00:15:37.940 --> 00:15:38.940
But,

00:15:39.810 --> 00:15:41.640
I will always be by Fuu's side.

00:15:44.140 --> 00:15:45.870
That much I can promise.

00:15:55.190 --> 00:15:58.600
Taking care of Fuu...
it's not that simple.

00:16:04.880 --> 00:16:06.080
Are you leaving already?

00:16:06.980 --> 00:16:08.180
I'll leave the rest to you.

00:16:11.280 --> 00:16:12.660
Why trust me?

00:16:17.440 --> 00:16:18.640
Because this is the first time

00:16:19.630 --> 00:16:21.540
Fuu has ever brought
someone here on this day.

00:16:57.740 --> 00:16:58.840
My dad...

00:16:59.650 --> 00:17:02.320
loved his son more than anyone in the
world.

00:17:03.700 --> 00:17:07.620
He was the kindest, coolest person ever.

00:17:14.960 --> 00:17:18.080
We don't have a grave for him.

00:17:22.370 --> 00:17:23.740
It was his final wish.

00:17:26.910 --> 00:17:28.890
His ashes were scattered at sea.

00:17:39.980 --> 00:17:41.550
But Fuu didn't agree with it.

00:17:43.280 --> 00:17:44.530
I still hate the idea.

00:17:46.550 --> 00:17:47.550
Because Fuu...

00:17:49.630 --> 00:17:50.799
Because even if he's just ashes,

00:17:50.800 --> 00:17:52.280
I still wanted him to be near me.

00:17:58.400 --> 00:17:59.400
I can't do this.

00:18:00.280 --> 00:18:02.090
I didn't want to cry in front of my dad.

00:18:06.160 --> 00:18:07.600
You've worked so hard, Fuu.

00:18:12.110 --> 00:18:13.740
I've seen it all along.

00:18:18.000 --> 00:18:19.900
I'm not doing well at all.

00:18:22.880 --> 00:18:24.590
I'm just pretending to be okay.

00:18:38.980 --> 00:18:40.570
Sorry for the late introduction.

00:18:42.790 --> 00:18:44.250
My name is Sara Kogami.

00:18:47.700 --> 00:18:49.890
My life has always felt empty.

00:18:51.930 --> 00:18:53.720
I had no goals, nothing I wanted to do.

00:18:55.590 --> 00:18:56.590
But...

00:18:57.320 --> 00:18:58.980
everything changed when I met Fuu.

00:19:01.380 --> 00:19:05.170
He gave me a reason to live.

00:19:11.850 --> 00:19:17.010
I'll spend the rest of my
life taking care of him.

00:19:32.370 --> 00:19:33.370
Fuu...

00:19:37.030 --> 00:19:38.030
I love you.

00:19:49.020 --> 00:19:50.120
Please...

00:19:50.580 --> 00:19:51.680
Just a little longer.

00:19:52.590 --> 00:19:53.860
Just a little more time...

00:19:55.050 --> 00:19:57.220
Please let me stay with him.

00:20:04.830 --> 00:20:06.890
Senpai, wait up!

00:20:07.550 --> 00:20:08.550
Senpai!

00:20:09.420 --> 00:20:10.420
Senpai!

00:20:11.080 --> 00:20:12.080
Senpai!

00:20:12.710 --> 00:20:13.810
When are you free next?

00:20:15.050 --> 00:20:17.169
You don't have class on Wednesday, right?

00:20:17.170 --> 00:20:19.580
I told you, I'm not going.

00:20:21.560 --> 00:20:22.860
Stop following me...

00:20:37.080 --> 00:20:38.080
Why?

00:20:40.740 --> 00:20:42.260
I've been chasing you this whole time.

00:20:44.220 --> 00:20:45.220
Huh?

00:20:45.930 --> 00:20:46.930
Well then...

00:20:47.170 --> 00:20:48.170
See you Monday.

00:21:16.650 --> 00:21:17.650
What's wrong?

00:21:19.260 --> 00:21:20.260
Can't sleep?

00:21:24.850 --> 00:21:25.850
At times like this...

00:21:26.730 --> 00:21:29.000
I usually go for a drive.

00:21:32.540 --> 00:21:34.530
But the engine is being repaired.

00:21:38.080 --> 00:21:39.560
Wasn't it just a scratch on the door?

00:21:41.500 --> 00:21:42.500
Huh?

00:21:43.630 --> 00:21:45.140
How did you know about the scratch?

00:21:47.140 --> 00:21:48.140
Hey!

00:21:48.380 --> 00:21:49.380
Hurry up!

00:21:49.960 --> 00:21:51.100
I'm working on it!

00:21:57.020 --> 00:21:58.020
What are you doing?

00:22:04.980 --> 00:22:08.090
So Sara-senpai was the
one protecting my car?

00:22:10.230 --> 00:22:11.230
Because...

00:22:11.460 --> 00:22:15.610
that car is a memento
of your father, right?

00:22:17.940 --> 00:22:18.940
But...

00:22:19.780 --> 00:22:20.890
why go to such lengths?

00:22:24.260 --> 00:22:26.140
I haven't done anything
for you, Sara-senpai...

00:22:36.620 --> 00:22:37.830
I don't need anything.

00:22:39.480 --> 00:22:40.480
Just...

00:22:44.280 --> 00:22:45.580
let me stay by your side.

00:27:11.640 --> 00:27:12.640
Fuu.

00:27:17.840 --> 00:27:18.840
What is it?

00:27:19.650 --> 00:27:20.910
Why didn't you wake me up?

00:27:26.310 --> 00:27:27.410
Please just go.

00:27:33.110 --> 00:27:34.110
If this keeps up...

00:27:34.570 --> 00:27:35.730
I won't be able to handle it.

00:27:37.440 --> 00:27:38.850
Please go back to your own world.

00:27:39.880 --> 00:27:40.880
Now.

00:27:47.320 --> 00:27:48.690
Fuu, do you want me to leave?

00:27:55.990 --> 00:27:58.070
But... it's the only way.

00:27:59.330 --> 00:28:00.330
I can't go back.

00:28:02.820 --> 00:28:04.520
There must be a way. If we just look...

00:28:04.960 --> 00:28:06.140
I'll help you.

00:28:09.340 --> 00:28:10.440
Why all of a sudden?

00:28:26.820 --> 00:28:28.800
The one you truly love...

00:28:29.670 --> 00:28:31.570
The one you want to take care of forever...

00:28:32.470 --> 00:28:33.670
isn't *this* Fuu, is it?

00:28:37.520 --> 00:28:40.140
The Fuu in the other world
lost his lover so suddenly...

00:28:40.530 --> 00:28:41.730
I know how he feels.

00:28:42.800 --> 00:28:44.600
Because I lost my dad, too.

00:28:45.720 --> 00:28:46.720
No, that's not it.

00:28:47.260 --> 00:28:48.030
Listen to me.

00:28:48.031 --> 00:28:49.670
I'm just a replacement.

00:28:51.170 --> 00:28:53.640
I shouldn't let myself fall for you.

00:29:00.860 --> 00:29:01.860
I'm sorry.

00:29:05.710 --> 00:29:07.320
There's something I have to tell you.

00:29:09.190 --> 00:29:10.190
No.

00:29:10.410 --> 00:29:11.410
I don't want to hear it.

00:29:14.190 --> 00:29:15.190
Fuu...

00:29:15.380 --> 00:29:16.380
Don't come any closer.

00:29:34.680 --> 00:29:35.680
Fuu!

00:29:47.050 --> 00:29:48.050
Sara-senpai?

00:29:51.160 --> 00:29:52.160
No!

00:29:52.560 --> 00:29:53.560
Sara-senpai!

00:29:53.930 --> 00:29:55.220
I don't want you to die.

00:29:58.550 --> 00:29:59.550
Wake up...

00:30:01.790 --> 00:30:02.850
Sara-senpai...

00:31:53.320 --> 00:31:54.320
Sara-senpai.

00:31:55.580 --> 00:31:56.680
Senpai, you're awake?

00:31:57.410 --> 00:31:58.410
Are you okay?

00:32:09.770 --> 00:32:10.770
Who are you?